Hello! Thank you for contacting Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. My name is William Henderson. How may I assist you with your shipping needs today?

Hi William. I'm curious about the shipping process. My name is Carolyn Brown.

Nice to meet you, Carolyn! I'm happy to help with any questions you might have. Are you looking to ship a recently purchased yacht?

Yes, exactly. I'm new to this, so I want to understand the process better.

Certainly, Carolyn. Could I start by getting the current location of your yacht?

It's currently in Fort Lauderdale, Florida.

Great, thank you. And where would you like your yacht shipped to?

I'd like it shipped to Newport, Rhode Island.

Perfect! We can arrange for a smooth transfer. We'll handle everything from logistics to ensuring your yacht is well-protected during transit.

Sounds good. Thank you for the information, William.

You're welcome, Carolyn! Thank you for choosing Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. If you need any more assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
